    "approach, which employed only half of the pre-trained target encoder [43].",
    "The methodology employed by the ELECTRA-DTA model aligns closely with our approach [36].",
    "In the ELECTRA-DTA framework, the features originating from the pre-trained drug encoder and protein encoder are individually averaged.",
    "Subsequently, these averaged features are compactly represented as a compressed feature vector.",
    "This vector is subsequently incorporated into a squeeze-andexcitation network, aiming to enhance the predictive capabilities of the model."
